\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 About The ScriptMenu Folder
\f1\b0\fs28 \

\fs24 \
The ScriptMenu folder (~/Library/Application Support/CotEditor/ScriptMenu/) is the folder for CotEditor's Script menu.\
\
On launching, CotEditor reads the script files in this folder (file extension: .applescript .scpt .sh .pl .php .rb .py) and make them appear in the Script menu.\
If you made modifications to the folder while CotEditor is running, you can manually update the menu by choosing Update Script Menu in the Script menu.\
\
